9. What are the most commonly used opacifying ingredients in the cosmetics industry?
Titanium dioxide and zinc oxide are commonly used opacifying ingredients in the cosmetics industry.

10. How are opacifying ingredients used in the food industry?
Opacifying ingredients are used in the food industry to improve the visual appearance and texture of products such as sauces, dressings, and dairy products.

